title: MBMBaM 436: Face 2 Face: I Had Charcuterie Today!
description: Join us and a rowdy crowd of wild Texans from our live show at the ACL Live at the Moody Theater as we discuss What’s-A Christmas to Me, Modern Day Knights and the art of arranging old, old meats and cheeses on slabs of ancient wood.
author: shows@mbmbam.com (Justin McElroy)
